===Noun===
'''reef''' ('''reefs''')

#A chain or range of rocks lying at or near the surface of the water. See [[coral reefs]].
#A large [[vein]] of [[auriferous]] [[quartz]]; -- so called in Australia. Hence, any body of rock yielding valuable ore.
#(''sailing'') a rope put in to make the sail smaller
#A [[reef knot]]

